All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
FileManager
Utility class to assist the Shop in reading and printing to predefined text files.
FrontEnd
Front end for the retail store application.
Inventory
Provides methods and data types to create a Inventory for the storage and management of Items.
Item
Provides methods and data types to create a Tool or Item for a shop.
Order
Provides methods and data fields to create an Order that stores and manages a list of order lines.
OrderLine
Provides data fields and methods to create a order line for items that need to be ordered.
Shop
Provides methods and data field to create a Shop for hosting an inventory of items and suppliers.
Supplier
Contains data fields and methods for creating a supplier to hold information about the supplier for an item.
SupplierList
Provides data fields and methods for creating a Supplier List for the storage and management of a list of suppliers.
